    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "📇 HUBSPOT CRM\n\n>>> API SETUP <<<\n1. https://app.hubspot.com (free)\n2. Settings → Integrations → Private Apps\n3. Create app: 'n8n Outreach Bot'\n4. Scopes:\n   • crm.objects.contacts.read\n   • crm.objects.contacts.write\n5. Copy access token\n\n>>> N8N CREDENTIAL <<<\nCredentials → Add → HubSpot App Token\n\n>>> CUSTOM PROPERTIES <<<\nCreate in HubSpot Settings → Properties:\n• subscriber_count (number)\n• niche (text)\n• linkedin_url (text)\n\nFREE: up to 1M contacts",
        "width": 400,
        "height": 300
      },
      "id": "d036b0b6-9e15-4d98-a33d-e9d4f3cb5bc6",
      "name": "Sticky Note - 📇 HUBSPOT CRM\n\n>>> ",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        2370,
        -120
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "agent": "conversationalAgent",
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Write a personalized cold email for CrowdWisdomTrading.\n\nABOUT US: CrowdWisdomTrading (www.crowdwisdomtrading.com) — trading community.\n\nLEAD INFO:\n• Name: {{ $json.name }}\n• Channel: {{ $json.channel_name }} ({{ $json.channel_url }})\n• Niche: {{ $json.niche }}\n• Topics: {{ $json.recent_topics }}\n• Subs: {{ $json.subscribers }}\n\nRULES:\n1. Subject: Hook about CrowdWisdomTrading\n2. Opening: Reference their content\n3. CTA: Ask for feedback on our platform\n4. Tone: Warm, trader-to-trader\n5. Max 150-200 words\n\nReturn JSON only:\n{\"subject\": \"...\", \"body\": \"...\", \"personalization_notes\": \"...\"}",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "Expert cold email writer for CrowdWisdomTrading. Write genuine, personalized emails. Reference specific recipient details. No generic templates."
        }
      },
      "id": "82193b41-5a3b-4747-93e1-2671d906930b",
      "name": "AI Write Email",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 1.7,
