      "parameters": {
        "content": "✉️ AI WRITE EMAIL\n\nSame LLM as Research node.\nAdd same Chat Model sub-node.\n\nOutput:\n• Subject line (about CWT)\n• Personalized body\n• CTA: ask for feedback\n\n✅ Reuses same LLM credential",
